Module dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform
Package dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform.math

Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform.math.Vector
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoundedVector
    public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object
    A vector defined as a head at some point in 3 dimensions and a tail at (0, 0, 0).
